DeSantis and Abbott lead pushback against vaccine mandates. U.S. Surgeon General Murthy: Vaxxed kids still need masks in school, Florida surgeon general pushes back. Data overwhelmingly proves masks in schools don't have any impact, hurt children. Dems panic as Youngkin pulls into dead heat with McAuliffe in Virginia.
